{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this is-- you know, in the worst of the moment of my survival, I always felt we are the sacrificial lamb for a better world to come.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But when I look around, [BACKGROUND NOISE] I don't see it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's very depressing that in our generation we are witnessing things which we thought will never happen again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this is why I feel what you are doing is important.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Not to tell my story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This is not important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I am just representing somebody from this generation, from this part of the world, who didn't choose to be born Jewish or didn't choose to be born Polish, but it was that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the price I had to pay for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I feel that only education can help.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Only people-- if they are aware what is happening anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we also have to be aware of what is happening now anywhere else-- can build a better world to come.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Because man is capable of terrible things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "At the same time, man is capable of very noble things, but it depends which part of-- is developed which time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I think that, if we are aware-- because very often, if you know about it when it's too late, you can't do anything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Nobody could have done very much, once you were in that situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But perhaps if we can see the signals and the symptoms to prevent it happening again, that perhaps our generation had some kind of a responsibility to do that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But, you know, I always had a difficult situation-- to talk, or not to talk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "To be, or not to be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was always with me, this conflict.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
